{"word":"G545 - ἀπειθής - apeithḗs - ap-i-thace' - Disobedient","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπειθής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apeithḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-i-thace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Disobedient</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கீழ்ப்படியாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"impersuasible, uncompliant, contumacious"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G3982 - πείθω - peíthō - pi'-tho/3982\">G3982</a>; <i>unpersuadable</i>, that is, <i>contumacious:</i> - disobedient.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3980/3980\">G3980</a>, <a href=\"#/G3981/3981\">G3981</a>, <a href=\"#/G3982/3982\">G3982</a>, <a href=\"#/G3988/3988\">G3988</a>, <a href=\"#/G4006/4006\">G4006</a>, <a href=\"#/G543/543\">G543</a>, <a href=\"#/G544/544\">G544</a>, <a href=\"#/G545/545\">G545</a>"}]}